---
import almaymenteImage from "../assets/almaymente.png";
---

<section id='ceo' class='ceo-section'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='ceo-wrapper'>
      <div class='ceo-content'>
        <span class='section-subtitle'>Innovación & Bienestar</span>
        <h2 class='ceo-title'>
          CEO de <span class='text-gradient'>Almaymente.io</span>
        </h2>
        <p class='lead'>
          Revolucionando el bienestar integral a través de la tecnología.
        </p>

        <div class='ceo-description'>
          <p>
            Como fundadora y CEO de <strong>Almaymente.io</strong>, lidero una
            plataforma pionera que fusiona la psicología clínica con la
            tecnología accesible. Nuestra misión es democratizar el acceso a
            herramientas de salud mental, ofreciendo un ecosistema digital donde
            el bienestar integral es la prioridad.
          </p>
          <p>
            Almaymente no es solo una plataforma; es un movimiento hacia una
            vida más consciente, equilibrada y plena.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href='https://www.almaymente.io'
          target='_blank'
          rel='noopener noreferrer'
          class='btn btn-primary'
        >
          Explorar Plataforma
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class='ceo-visual'>
        <div class='glow-orb'></div>
        <div class='device-mockup'>
          <img
            src={almaymenteImage.src}
            alt='Almaymente.io Platform'
            class='screenshot-img'
          />
          <div class='screen-overlay'></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ceo-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      #000000 0%,
      var(--bg-secondary) 50%,
      #000000 100%
    );
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Grid background with glow */
  .ceo-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: linear-gradient(
        rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.05) 1px,
        transparent 1px
      ),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ceo-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .ceo-title {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #999);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .ceo-description {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .ceo-description p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ceo-visual {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .glow-orb {
    position: absolute;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2) 0%,
      rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 40%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    filter: blur(100px);
    animation: pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.6;
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }
  }

  .device-mockup {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2),
      0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
      0 0 80px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .device-mockup:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.4),
      0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8),
      0 0 120px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
  }

  .screenshot-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .screen-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.05) 0%,
      transparent 50%,
      rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 100%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .device-mockup:hover .screen-overlay {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ceo-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .ceo-visual {
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .tech-circle,
    .tech-circle-inner {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      max-height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
